- Anything you need.
- I need you to be fair.

211
00:08:37,884 --> 00:08:41,403
- Fair?
- Yes, fair.

212
00:08:41,488 --> 00:08:43,823
- That's one way to go.
- It's <i>the</i> way to go...

213
00:08:43,890 --> 00:08:46,242
Because I need them to think
that we're moving on,

214
00:08:46,326 --> 00:08:48,744
when, in fact,
we're going after their clients.

215
00:08:48,829 --> 00:08:51,563
Oh, my God.
Oh, my God.

216
00:08:51,615 --> 00:08:53,199
