on one of your missions?

217
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:55,668
This is Litt-tastic.
Louis, calm down.

218
00:08:55,735 --> 00:08:56,869
Calm down?
No!

219
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:58,337
This is just like
<i>The Great Escape.</i>

220
00:08:58,404 --> 00:08:59,839
